:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QZm8DnYyQl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQZm8DnYyQl0&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e800acb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QZm8DnYyQl0</a><br />\n我諗本身劉備落既命令係有比關羽打上去<br />\n由漢中之戰左右開始一直侵擾曹操<br />\n拖住曹操d兵唔可以上去漢中<br />\n可能後尾打得太勁,令東吳覺得有威脅而背盟<br />\n劉備諸葛都未必估到最後會咁.."},{"pid":"baf27c2e4c2d2d4249318d046ee525a908a57f75","tid":2186754,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:37:33.000Z","msg":"陸遜做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537ca11e85139b38139f76e51bd9e0aeed508b58","tid":2186754,"uid":5502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2c7291d6971166ee3da285518069efc3b08b6c9c","tid":2186754,"uid":85675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QZm8DnYyQl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQZm8DnYyQl0&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hVDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e800acb2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QZm8DnYyQl0</a><br />\n我諗本身劉備落既命令係有比關羽打上去<br />\n由漢中之戰左右開始一直侵擾曹操<br />\n拖住曹操d兵唔可以上去漢中<br />\n可能後尾打得太勁,令東吳覺得有威脅而背盟<br />\n劉備諸葛都未必估到最後會咁.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:41:24.000Z","msg":"東吳想打荊州好耐，關羽都有準備軍隊係江陵<br />\n係聽到呂蒙病重既消息先&quot;稍撤兵以赴樊&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而且後方江陵、公安經過關羽多年經營，城防堅固，如果唔係糜芳士仁投降，江陵、公安唔會咁易失守"},{"pid":"145f5db3ba76f509513ad768b4788e67cd9bcdae","tid":2186754,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"結果論黎睇<br />\n孫吳同曹一齊夾蜀<br />\n拎左荊州<br />\n但同時都令蜀積弱最後降埋魏最後自己滅埋國<br />\n反而自己拎完地又冇出力北上抗曹"},{"pid":"a4a520caf0dcc7f97706d31b245b6552460fd7bb","tid":2186754,"uid":15830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"145f5db3ba76f509513ad768b4788e67cd9bcdae","tid":2186754,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T08:43:45.000Z","msg":"結果論黎睇<br />\n孫吳同曹一齊夾蜀<br />\n拎左荊州<br />\n但同時都令